OL,6,FThe Environment Department (Defra)
OL,7,Fsaid the government will also launch a
OL,8,Fconsultation later this year on
OL,9,Fproposals to reform bathing water
OL,10,Fregulations in England.
OL,12,FThis includes proposed change to drive
OL,13,Fimprovements to water quality at
OL,14,Fbathing spots, enhance monitoring and
OL,15,Fenable more flexibility around the
OL,16,Fdates of the monitoring season.
