OL,6,FDefra said it will seek public and
OL,7,Fstakeholder views on extending the
OL,8,Fdefinition of "bathers" to include a
OL,9,Fwider range of water users beyond
OL,10,Fswimmers ` such as rowers, kayakers
OL,11,Fand paddle boarders.
OL,13,FDefra said that last year 96% of
OL,14,Fbathing waters in England met minimum
OL,15,Fannual standards and 90% were rated as
OL,16,F"good" or "excellent".
