OL,6,FBut there has been over the state of
OL,7,FEngland's rivers and coastal waters,
OL,8,Fwhich suffer pollution from sewage
OL,9,Foutlets and other sources such as
OL,10,Fagricultural run-off.
OL,12,FThe new bathing waters include a dozen
OL,13,Friver sites like the Severn at
OL,14,FIronbridge, and Wallingford Beach on
OL,15,Fthe River Thames in Berkshire.
OL,17,FIn addition, several spots on Coniston
OL,18,FWater and one on Derwent Water, in
OL,19,FCumbria, have been added as designated
OL,20,Fspots.
