OL,6,FMaking the announcement on what was
OL,7,Fdescribed as the largest ever rollout
OL,8,Fof new bathing sites, water minister
OL,9,FRobbie Moore said: "The value our
OL,10,Fbathing waters bring to local
OL,11,Fcommunities is incredibly valuable `
OL,12,Fproviding social, physical and
OL,13,Fpositive health and wellbeing benefits
OL,14,Fto people around the country ` and I
OL,15,Fam pleased to have approved a further
OL,16,F27 new bathing water sites for this
OL,17,Fyear.
