OL,6,F"I am fully committed to seeing the
OL,7,Fquality of our coastal waters, rivers
OL,8,Fand lakes rise further for the benefit
OL,9,Fof the environment and everyone who
OL,10,Fuses them."
OL,12,FAlan Lovell, Environment Agency
OL,13,Fchairman, said: "Overall bathing water
OL,14,Fquality has improved massively over
OL,15,Fthe last decade due to targeted and
OL,16,Frobust regulation from the Environment
OL,17,FAgency, and the good work carried out
OL,18,Fby partners and local groups.
